headline: Principal to Announce First Quarter 2025 Financial Results
summary: DES MOINES, Iowa, April 03, 2025--Principal Financial Group® (Nasdaq: PFG) announced today that it will release first quarter 2025 financial results after U.S. markets close on Thursday, April 24, 2025.
